  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The use of NPWT as a post-operative dressing significantly reduces the incidence of seroma
      formation after harvesting LD flap.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      NPWT was left in place on donor site with constant pressure between -125 and -80 mmHg to
      reduce seroma formation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
